history.title: Tungsten materials in the solid form having all of the following:

supplement.heading: Supplement No. 1 to Part 774 - The Commerce Control List

breadcrumbs: C. “Materials”

1C117 Materials for the fabrication of missile “parts” or “components” for rockets or missiles capable of achieving a “range” equal to or greater than 300 km, as follows (see List of Items Controlled).
history.text:
Tungsten materials in the solid form having all of the following:
Any of the following material compositions:
c.1. Any of the following material compositions:
Tungsten and alloys containing 97% by weight or more of tungsten;
c.1.a. Tungsten and alloys containing 97% by weight or more of tungsten;
Copper infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; or
c.1.b. Copper infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; or
Silver infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; and
c.1.c. Silver infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; and
Able to be machined to any of the following products:
c.2. Able to be machined to any of the following products:
Cylinders having a diameter of 120 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater;
c.2.a. Cylinders having a diameter of 120 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater;
Tubes having an inner diameter of 65 mm or greater and a wall thickness of 25 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater; or
c.2.b. Tubes having an inner diameter of 65 mm or greater and a wall thickness of 25 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater; or
Blocks having a size of 120 mm × 120 mm × 50 mm or greater.
c.2.c. Blocks having a size of 120 mm × 120 mm × 50 mm or greater.

supplement.heading: Supplement No. 1 to Part 774 - The Commerce Control List

breadcrumbs: C. “Materials”

1C117 Materials for the fabrication of missile “parts” or “components” for rockets or missiles capable of achieving a “range” equal to or greater than 300 km, as follows (see List of Items Controlled).
history.text:
Tungsten materials in the solid form having all of the following:
Any of the following material compositions:
c.1. Any of the following material compositions:
Tungsten and alloys containing 97% by weight or more of tungsten;
c.1.a. Tungsten and alloys containing 97% by weight or more of tungsten;
Copper infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; or
c.1.b. Copper infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; or
Silver infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; and
c.1.c. Silver infiltrated tungsten containing 80% by weight or more of tungsten; and
Able to be machined to any of the following products:
c.2. Able to be machined to any of the following products:
Cylinders having a diameter of 120 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater;
c.2.a. Cylinders having a diameter of 120 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater;
Tubes having an inner diameter of 65 mm or greater and a wall thickness of 25 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater; or
c.2.b. Tubes having an inner diameter of 65 mm or greater and a wall thickness of 25 mm or greater and a length of 50 mm or greater; or
Blocks having a size of 120 mm × 120 mm × 50 mm or greater.
c.2.c. Blocks having a size of 120 mm × 120 mm × 50 mm or greater.
